This paper proposes a method to regularize the structures of Deep Neural Networks (DNNs) to reduce computation cost and improve classification accuracy. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Machine Learning (cs.LG), Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE), and Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS).
